>\n<br />\n大家繼續幫手文宣 各自爬山 山頂見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbeb9b6619b57996cec4ffea4778ce245bc7d59d","tid":1354372,"uid":48679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:51:56.000Z","msg":"727元朗, 全部諗緊唔好去,叫緊其他人唔好去既同我入黎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1352206\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1352206</a>"},{"pid":"13a55dc85e045efb8713dcd313b51b06d29ff789","tid":1354372,"uid":264336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:52:31.000Z","msg":"八鄉李漢民 爛仔做差人"},{"pid":"091ea75d60c4bacd713cb99b58da6fbfc96159dc","tid":1354372,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:54:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354118</a><br />\n<br />\n幫推 用罷免何妖嚟成立新議會"},{"pid":"091cdc4d74690c49ad8b115a03b4be213f836003","tid":1354372,"uid":264336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:55:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6cf19d0a242d10cb651776706a6fa1a3fce6ccb1","tid":1354372,"uid":264336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:01:56.000Z","msg":"Push push"},{"pid":"2a8bda3e859ec55a29eeba03f01b23f079a3b95d","tid":1354372,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c97d10de3a7497a7ee211c736d4c78fccf27d626","tid":1354372,"uid":23707,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFqibUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFqibUD.jpg&h=ebc0d1d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qRtS0NX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqRtS0NX.jpg&h=7578d7a1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n十八鄉連儂牆準備上線啦!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-